{
  "stem": "7094.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Not once did they put on a foreign station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "This is the obedience.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They're following the laws.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, they were very obedient, before, through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also-- a lot of it, also, later on, came-- they didn't talk about a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, because-- children at home and other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, certain subjects were not talked-- probably they was also frightened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were all very patriotic and obedient.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they didn't confront the extermination.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They thought that these people were sent back, you know-- that they live somewhere in the camp, and they're working.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There started another problem for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because having Ukrainian document as Olga Demczyzszak-- as I told you, Ukrainian had certain privileges-- not many.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't experience many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I had to go, then, to a Ukrainian-- the Ukrainian had a sort of embassy there, in Berlin, and I had to go there and to pass a certificate that I'm Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought I'll never do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I could fib along with the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I could-- could-- could talk like-- But there, to pass a test for Ukrainian, I never thought I'll do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Again, I had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they talked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They examined.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they didn't suspect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they would have delved a little bit deeper, they could have found out, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I spoke Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they just didn't-- it didn't occur to them to investigate it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they just saw the documents, gave me the certificate, and I came home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I worked there for about a year, I think-- yes-- as a domestic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was a privileged family, in a way, because mostly German were entitled-- when you had four children.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
